          "datePublished": "2020-07-06",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best school of my life. I am proud to be a CLARETINE\n\nThe teachers are very helpful. They guide the students in all possible way. The school has laboratories of Physics, Chemistry, Biology, Computer and a large library. The play ground is very big. There is also a big basketball court. A lot of playing equipments are also present. The school is from nursery to XII. Our principal is a caring person. He loves us a lot and cares for us. He listens to our problems and gives solutions to that. He is a very friendly man. He often takes us to trip to various educational places and organises various sports event in our school. He is a man with amazing qualities.\n\nWe all love our school, teachers, principal and all the other staffs.\n\nOnce again proud to be a CLARETINE.\n\nProud of my school.\n\n\"EAST OR WEST ST. CLARET IS THE BEST!!\"\n\nStarting this journey on 2010 I have completed ten years here. I want to be a part of this family for ever and spend the rest of the two years of my school life in this school only.\n\nThis is the best and most memorable journey ever encountered by me.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
